{"type": "article", "id": 26964, "title": "无限度量仪", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-18T07:23:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144015qmEo5W0Uls6bTuwa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>2015 年红点设计奖的<a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/en/online-exhibition/infinite-ruler/\">获奖作品</a>，由 Yang Fan 等人设计的 Infinite Ruler 打算重新定义“度量”，让你不用再依赖传统的卷尺。这个戒指造型的智能度量仪打破了卷尺的限制，可以测量任何长度的物品，并将数字显示在顶部的界面上。它的操作方式非常简单，在测量起点按下后将物品从界面下方划过，在终点松开即可。戒指内侧使用了可延展的材质，能够适应手指的不同粗细。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144013coVN5mIXUQaEzwDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.53238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144014HD9w5yOfzmx0GbJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144014uFOkZwtVaGJY65Xg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144015CuLtD5oE39lpT1YR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}